  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 15th level, your binding with this curse has fundamentally changed you.</p><p> But it has also made you see the true value in numbers.</p><p> As a reaction, you may interpose an attack targeting an ally within your movement speed.</p><p> You move between the attacker and your ally and become the new target of the attack.</p><p> When you do this, you gain resistance to the damage type of the triggering attack until the start of your next turn.</p><p> Taking damage in this way cannot reduce your Hit Points to 0.</p><p></p>",
